About Shawerma ElReem

Founded in 2007, Shawerma ElReem was the first brand under SAB Holdings and one of the earliest shawerma chains in Egypt. Built on authentic Levantine flavors, ElReem became a household name known for consistency, affordability, and cultural relevance.

16+ Stores • Part of SAB Holdings
